    <item>
      <title>当Sheinbaum押注美国交易时，墨西哥保持关税报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/mexico-holds-off-tariff-retaliation-as-sheinbaum-bets-on-us-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥推迟了对美国对钢铁和铝制进口的关税的反应，因为总统克劳迪娅·辛巴姆（Claudia Sheinbaum）避免了报复，而两国则谈判避免在广泛的产品和服务上征收征税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/mexico-holds-off-tariff-retaliation-as-sheinbaum-bets-on-us-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 17:20:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鸡蛋价格在60％激增后放弃时会放松</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/eggs-continued-a-surge-in-february-but-price-relief-is-at-hand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在过去的一年中近60％的增长使购物者不愿意购买之后，美国鸡蛋价格终于显示出缓解的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/eggs-continued-a-surge-in-february-but-price-relief-is-at-hand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 14:41:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>顶级石油交易者的价格上涨，看到过度供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/oil-traders-turn-bearish-on-prices-seeing-global-oversupply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[休斯顿大型年度石油和天然气聚会的情绪使该行业的前景令人振奋，这是对化石燃料友好的特朗普政府的发展。但是有一个很大的收获：一些最大的石油交易商在原油价格的前景上变得更加看跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/oil-traders-turn-bearish-on-prices-seeing-global-oversupply</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 14:05:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国债券拒绝冷却器通货膨胀数据随着关税的担忧而占主导地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/us-bonds-shrug-off-cooler-inflation-with-fed-cut-views-intact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国库在一次动荡的交易中倒下，因为随着全球贸易战的加深贸易战争的恢复掩盖了美国通货膨胀报告的凉爽。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/us-bonds-shrug-off-cooler-inflation-with-fed-cut-views-intact</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 13:02:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票拉力赛随着关税通货膨胀路径的关税而逐渐减弱：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
